      "description": "Offering a collector-grade E46 M3 in concours condition. This example features the legendary S54 inline-six, benefiting from a proactive VANOS overhaul and rear subframe reinforcement. The 6-speed Getrag manual transmission shifts with clinical precision, sending power through a factory limited-slip differential. The suspension retains its original geometry with fresh bushings throughout, ensuring the telepathic turn-in these chassis are known for. Every individual throttle body is synchronized for instantaneous response. Meticulously preserved with a documented service history, this is a turn-key specimen for the high-performance purist.",
