      "id": "sybil_9_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional, collector-grade vehicle that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. This car has been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage and has never seen a single snowflake or raindrop. The exterior finish is breathtaking, featuring a deep, mirror-like shine with a professional ceramic coating and absolutely zero rock chips, door dings, or scratches. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom state; the premium leather seats are firm with no bolster wear, the original carpets are pristine, and it still retains that distinct new-car scent. Mechanically, it is flawless. Every service has been performed ahead of schedule at the authorized dealership, with a complete thick folder of records included. It features low original miles, brand-new tires, and both original key fobs. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning buyer to own a perfect example of this model. Serious inquiries only for this turn-key masterpiece.",
